---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { NAV_ITEMS } from '@data/navigation';
import Timeline from '@components/ui/Timeline.astro';
import SectionHeader from '@components/ui/SectionHeader.astro';
import ParticleField from '@components/interactive/ParticleField.astro';
import MistEffect from '@components/interactive/MistEffect.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="灵墟 - 末法时代·失落修行文明档案馆">
  <ParticleField />
  <MistEffect />

  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#050505] via-[#080808] to-[#080808]"></div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div class="sacred-geometry -top-20 -left-20 animate-twinkle" style="animation-delay: 0s;"></div>
      <div class="sacred-geometry -bottom-40 -right-20 animate-twinkle" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
      <div class="sacred-geometry top-1/3 right-1/4 animate-twinkle" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="mb-12 animate-fade-in">
        <div class="relative inline-block">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full border border-[#c9a227]/30 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto animate-float-gentle glow-border">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-[#d4af37]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border border-[#c9a227]/10 scale-125 animate-pulse"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl font-display text-[#e8d48b] mb-6 tracking-[0.15em] animate-slide-up text-shadow-gold">
        灵墟
      </h1>

      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.15s;">
        <div class="h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-[#c9a227]/50"></div>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-[#c9a227]/80 font-light tracking-[0.3em]">
          末法时代
        </p>
        <div class="h-px w-16 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-[#c9a227]/50"></div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-lg text-[#888888] mb-16 tracking-wider animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.25s;">
        失落修行文明档案馆
      </p>

      <div class="gold-line max-w-md mx-auto mb-12 animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;"></div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-[#666666] max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 leading-loose animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        <p>天地灵气衰竭，法脉传承断绝。</p>
        <p>唯有典籍文字，传其余绪。</p>
        <p class="text-[#c9a227]/60 text-sm tracking-widest">此处乃禁毁档案，慎入。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.65s;">
        <a
          href="/archive"
          class="group relative px-10 py-4 rounded-lg overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105"
        >
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c9a227]/20 via-[#d4af37]/10 to-[#c9a227]/20 border border-[#c9a227]/40 rounded-lg"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#c9a227]/5 to-transparent"></div>
          <span class="relative text-[#d4af37] tracking-widest group-hover:text-shadow-gold transition-all">
            进入档案馆
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#intro"
          class="group px-10 py-4 rounded-lg border border-[#333333]/60 text-[#666666] hover:text-[#c9a227] hover:border-[#444444] transition-all duration-500"
        >
          <span class="tracking-wider">了解更多</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-float-gentle">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-[#c9a227]/30">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest">向下探索</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-40 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#080808] to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
  </section>

  <section id="intro" class="py-32 px-6 sm:px-8 relative">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="项目缘起"
        description="在末法的黄昏，追寻失落的修行文明"
        section="关于"
      />

      <div class="mt-16 prose-lingxu max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p>
          灵墟，取"灵炁墟烬"之意，是一个关于中国修行文明的数字档案馆。
          我们试图在典籍、宗教、民俗、传说与小说之间，勾勒出一个曾经真实存在过的修行世界。
        </p>

        <h2>末法时代的来临</h2>
        <p>
          据古籍记载，天地灵气曾充沛于世。上古真人可乘天地之正，御六气之辩。
          修行者能够以肉身通神，以精魄游太虚。然而，随着末法时代的降临，灵炁衰竭，
          上古真法渐失其传，留存于世的唯有残缺的典籍与口耳相传的传说。
        </p>

        <h2>档案的重建</h2>
        <p>
          灵墟致力于收集、整理、研究散落于各处的修行文明碎片：
          从《黄帝内经》探索身体与能量的奥秘，从《山海经》追溯神怪异兽的真相，
          从佛道典籍中梳理法脉传承的脉络，从志怪小说中还原修行境界的演化。
        </p>

        <blockquote>
          "夫道者，覆天载地，廓四方，柝八极，高不可际，深不可测。"
          <cite class="block mt-3 text-[#888888] not-italic text-sm">——《庄子·大宗师》</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          这不是游戏攻略，也不是玄幻小说设定集。
          这是一个严肃的、关于真实历史与文化中被遗忘之物的档案项目。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 sm:px-8 relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[#0a0a0a]/50 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="六大时代"
        description="从鸿蒙开辟到末法降临，修行文明的兴衰轮回"
        section="时间线"
      />

      <div class="mt-16">
        <Timeline />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 sm:px-8 relative">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="探索板块"
        description="五大领域，涵盖修行文明的各个面向"
        section="导航"
      />

      <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        {NAV_ITEMS.map((item, index) => (
          <a
            href={item.href}
            class="section-card group block"
            style={`animation-delay: ${index * 0.1}s`}
          >
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-display text-[#e8c76b] group-hover:text-[#f0d78c] transition-all duration-300 tracking-wide">
                {item.label}
              </h3>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#c9a227]/40 group-hover:text-[#d4af37] group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[#888888] group-hover:text-[#a0a0a0] transition-colors leading-relaxed">
              {item.description}
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-[#2a2a2a]/50">
              <span class="text-xs text-[#c9a227]/50 tracking-widest group-hover:text-[#c9a227]/80 transition-colors">探索更多 →</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 px-6 sm:px-8 relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[#0a0a0a]/50 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <SectionHeader
        title="档案精选"
        description="来自各板块的核心文献"
        section="推荐阅读"
      />

      <div class="mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/archive/end-of-dharma-age" class="section-card group block">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-widest text-[#c9a227]/70 border border-[#c9a227]/20 rounded-full mb-4">档案馆</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display text-[#e8c76b] mt-2 group-hover:text-[#f0d78c]">末法时代的真相</h3>
          <p class="text-[#888888] mt-4 group-hover:text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
            探讨末法时代的起源、特征及其对修行文明的深远影响
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#c9a227]/50 tracking-widest">阅读全文 →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/medicine/huangdi-neijing" class="section-card group block">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-widest text-[#2d8a8a]/70 border border-[#2d8a8a]/20 rounded-full mb-4">医药</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display text-[#5ababa] mt-2 group-hover:text-[#7ad4d4]">黄帝内经与修行身体</h3>
          <p class="text-[#888888] mt-4 group-hover:text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
            从医学经典探索古人对人体能量系统的理解
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#2d8a8a]/50 tracking-widest">阅读全文 →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/myth/shanhai-overview" class="section-card group block">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-widest text-[#8a4a2d]/70 border border-[#8a4a2d]/20 rounded-full mb-4">神话</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display text-[#ba7a5a] mt-2 group-hover:text-[#d4946a]">山海经：失落的地理</h3>
          <p class="text-[#888888] mt-4 group-hover:text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
            将山海经重新诠释为失落时代的地理档案
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#8a4a2d]/50 tracking-widest">阅读全文 →</div>
        </a>

        <a href="/dharma/buddhism-and-daoism" class="section-card group block">
          <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs tracking-widest text-[#6b4a8a]/70 border border-[#6b4a8a]/20 rounded-full mb-4">法脉</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display text-[#a878b8] mt-2 group-hover:text-[#c494d4]">佛道述略</h3>
          <p class="text-[#888888] mt-4 group-hover:text-[#a0a0a0] leading-relaxed">
            佛教东渐与道教兴起的修行传承脉络
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#6b4a8a]/50 tracking-widest">阅读全文 →</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 px-6 text-center relative">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="gold-line mb-12 max-w-xs mx-auto"></div>
      <p class="text-[#555555] tracking-wider leading-loose">
        灵墟 · 末法时代失落修行文明档案馆<br/>
        <span class="text-sm text-[#444444]">愿见者得度，闻者觉悟</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
